22 | ### 2. ArduPilotPlugin (SDF Plugin)
23 | - **Location:** Embedded in [`worlds/ardupilot_humanoid.sdf`](worlds/ardupilot_humanoid.sdf)
24 | - **JSON Protocol:** 127.0.0.1:9002
25 | - **Data Flow:**
26 |   - **IN:** IMU data from Gazebo → ArduPilot
27 |   - **OUT:** Servo PWM from ArduPilot → Joint angles
28 | - **PWM Conversion Formula:** `angle = (pwm - 1500) / 500 * multiplier + offset`
29 | - **Channel Mapping (4 channels only):**
30 |   - CH0 → l_hip_pitch (mult=1.571, offset=-0.5)
